unittitle_ssm: Records of the Office of Research Services/Office of Sponsored Programs
abstract_ssm: These Research Administration Papers incorporate materials generated during the years 1940-2005, including selected and duplicated material created 1940-1946 in the Office of Chancellor Harry Woodburn Chase, within other university units, and within the Office of Research Services 1952-1971, and its renamed successor Office of Sponsored Programs 1971-2005. The Papers have been divided into six series.
